{"tid":376551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【20萬點擊】台女公務員洩八爪椅性愛片 前男友被判刑","createTime":"2017-08-27T05:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T14:47:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a43547b2c167048f331e84ff4e7c500a89d6c4b","tid":376551,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170827/large/1503806724_a0ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170827%2Flarge%2F1503806724_a0ad.jpg&h=4f61dcd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n性愛影片遭上傳，台灣女公務員迄今痛不欲生。<br />\n<br />\n據台灣《自由時報》報道，女公務員小美（化名）與俞姓前男友上汽車旅館拍下一段「八爪椅性愛影片」，遭上傳國際色情網站，被當成免費熱門A片，長期供人下載，精神受重創、痛苦異常的小美提告，俞男否認上傳影片，並通過測謊。<br />\n但高等法院認定俞是「唯一擁有性愛影片者」，且上傳時間與懷疑小美另結新歡提分手的時間點吻合，將俞男判刑3月確定。性愛影片被上傳國外的色情網站，刑事局曾請求該網站提供上傳者帳號資料、傳輸時間等，未獲回覆。該段影片一直被放在網站上，迄昨已有19萬1898人次瀏覽。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"126619b73a516dbbc5459780a502497c384f29ac","tid":376551,"uid":53105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"39e33abe6a5bcb7cf0190e2037efdb4c73d29733","tid":376551,"uid":137768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2417b88b44a8946a4eb405897df6d53b299d72f","tid":376551,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌</blockquote><br />\nC9又樣衰..."},{"pid":"201f192ca4e758041f111bfa1ef7af386b13d390","tid":376551,"uid":84032,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:50:43.000Z","msg":"通過測謊無效用咁測乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acbd394c6c1342fa29bd6b21e72c9505f63f4a2","tid":376551,"uid":99175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockqu